Subject: Website is not opening although we add the full website in allowlist
Description: Website "https://indiankanoon.org/" is not opening although we whitelisted this website in allowlist with mentioned below *.indiankanoon.org* *.indiankanoon.com* Attached the showing DLP error
What_We_Know__c:
Adding mentioned below website details in allowed URL list in “URL Categories” under Denylists and Allowlists resolved the issue.

*.indiankanoon.org*
*.indiankanoon.com*
Solution_Comment__c:
